## Project Layout

```txt
src/
  bun/                  # Electrobun Bun process
  shared/               # Types shared by Bun and renderer
  views/main/           # {{frontendDisplayName}} renderer
```

Start replacing the starter UI in `{{homeFilePath}}`.

Native desktop code belongs in `src/bun`. Renderer code belongs in `src/views/main`. Shared payload types belong in `src/shared`.

## Native Bridge

{{#if hasElectrobunRpc}}
Typed RPC is enabled. The contract lives in `src/shared/rpc/schema.ts`, Bun handlers live in `src/bun/rpc`, and the renderer client lives in `src/views/main/lib/rpc.ts`.
{{else}}
RPC is disabled. The renderer is loaded as a static WebView surface with no generated native bridge.
{{/if}}
{{#if hasRpcExample}}

## RPC Example

The starter greeting/logging demo shows the full native bridge path:

- Shared RPC types: `src/shared/rpc/schema.ts`
- Bun handlers: `src/bun/rpc/router.ts`
- Renderer client: `src/views/main/lib/rpc.ts`
- Demo UI: `{{homeFilePath}}`
{{/if}}
